data.meta_description: Rebecca Young Mutterspaw was born on April 18, 1866 in Rockbridge, Virginia, United States, daughter of James F Muterspaugh and Sarah Ann Hughes. She died on June 23, 1954 in Rockbridge, Virginia, United States. This information is part of McDonald Wilton family tree- black  Hebrew  Yahya family line 1 by Dr Wilton McDonald- black Hebrew on Genealogy Online.
